    "Moreover, ChatGPT may lead to outline inconsistent performance which in turn may affect the reliability and validity of research findings [49].",
    "Figure 7 (a) and (b) shows that ChatGPT offered five articles related to each topic that was asked for.",
    "For the two ideas that ChatGPT suggested, the authors and years are the same, also the articles don't exist.• Difficulty to adopt new models: ChatGPT can be integrated to develop a new system.",
